      "parameters": {
        "width": 350,
        "height": 180,
        "content": "## üìä STEP 1: Invoice Data Collection\n\nThis workflow monitors overdue invoices from Google Sheets:\n\n1. **Get Rows**: Pulls invoice data from your tracking spreadsheet\n2. **Edit Fields**: Calculates days since invoice was sent using date difference\n3. **Filter**: Only processes invoices that are 7, 14, 21, or 28 days overdue\n\n**Setup**: Your Google Sheet needs columns for Date Sent, Client Name, Email, and Invoice ID"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-note-2",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        850,
        -150
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 380,
        "height": 200,
        "content": "## üîç STEP 2: Email History Intelligence\n\nPrevents sending follow-ups at inappropriate times:\n\n1. **Loop Over Items**: Processes each overdue invoice individually\n2. **Gmail Get Messages**: Retrieves recent email history with each client\n3. **Aggregate**: Combines email threads for AI analysis\n4. **Edit Fields**: Formats conversation data with timestamps\n\n**Key**: This step ensures you don't send follow-ups too soon after recent communication"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-note-3",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1500,
        -170
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 400,
        "height": 220,
        "content": "## üß† STEP 3: AI-Powered Follow-up Generation\n\nCreates intelligent, context-aware follow-up emails:\n\n**OpenAI Processing:**\n‚Ä¢ Analyzes conversation history to determine if follow-up is appropriate\n‚Ä¢ Selects template based on days overdue (7, 14, 21, 28-day intervals)\n‚Ä¢ Customizes message tone from gentle reminders to more urgent requests\n‚Ä¢ Returns verdict (true/false) and personalized email content\n\n**Templates**: 4 escalating follow-up templates with increasing urgency"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-note-4",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        2100,
        -150
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 380,
        "height": 200,
        "content": "## üìß STEP 4: Automated Email Delivery\n\nSends personalized follow-ups automatically:\n\n1. **Filter**: Only proceeds with emails that AI approved (verdict = true)\n2. **Gmail Draft/Send**: Creates professional follow-up emails with:\n   ‚Ä¢ Personalized subject lines\n   ‚Ä¢ Context-aware messaging\n   ‚Ä¢ Appropriate urgency level\n   ‚Ä¢ Professional but friendly tone\n\n**Result**: Clients receive timely, intelligent follow-ups that feel personally written"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
